Class MyStack<E>

java.lang.Object
implementations.MyStack<E>
Type Parameters:
E -
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, StackADT<E>
public class MyStack<E> extends Object implements StackADT<E>
A generic stack implementation using an array list. This class supports typical stack operations such as push, pop, peek, and checking if the stack is empty or full.
